<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Authentication Request</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Figtree", sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #00a2ff;
      }
      a {
        color: #00a2ff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #777;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Hotel Review Platform Authentication</h1>
    <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
    <p>
      We received a request to authenticate your account on Hotel Review Platform. To
      proceed and complete the authentication, please click the link below:
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="http://localhost:5173/verify/<%= code %>/<%= to %>">Authenticate Now</a>
    </p>
    <p>
      This link will automatically authenticate your account and allow you to
      access all the features of our site.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you did not request authentication, please ignore this message, and
      your account will remain secure.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you need any assistance or have any questions, feel free to reach out
      to our support team at
      <a href="mailto:mail@gmail.com">mail@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Best regards, <br />
      The Hotel Review Platform Team
    </p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        This email was sent by Hotel Review Platform. If you have any issues or
        questions, please contact us at the email above.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>